ly the localization technique to the first realization of free fields of A(1)1.To achieve the purpose, we introduced the Kac-Moody algebras, having the main focus the af-fine Kac-Moody algebras, according to [14]. Following, we defined the Verma modules, highlighting imaginary Verma modules of affine Lie algebra A(1)1, according to [8].", "Data de Publicação": "2017-11-16", "url": "http://www.teses.usp.br/teses/disponiveis/45/45131/tde-29092017-114301/pt-br.php"}
